mind is the part of you

00:04:05.670 --> 00:04:07.410 align:middle line:84%
that digests your
meals and keeps

00:04:07.410 --> 00:04:10.050 align:middle line:84%
your heart beating and
your lungs breathing

00:04:10.050 --> 00:04:12.180 align:middle line:90%
